Interface StatementBuilder.BuildableStatement

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ProcedureCall.OngoingStandaloneCallWithArguments, ProcedureCall.OngoingStandaloneCallWithoutArguments, ProcedureCall.OngoingStandaloneCallWithReturnFields, StatementBuilder.OngoingMatchAndReturnWithOrder, StatementBuilder.OngoingReadingAndReturn, StatementBuilder.OngoingUpdate, StatementBuilder.TerminalOngoingOrderDefinition

    public static interface StatementBuilder.BuildableStatement
    A statement that has all information required to be build and exposes a build method.
